arm_bot_base:
=============

Package contains all the scripts and launch files to be run on the Turtlebot 2 platform.
Distance sensing and colour blob detection can be performed with the use of any openni/openni2 supported 3d camera.

##Usage:

* "colors" folder is a container for profiles which are invoked by cmvision
* "launch" folder contains all the launch files required to initialize the Arm_Bot
* "param" folder contains the ROS navigation parameters for the robot
* "scripts" folder contains the nodes used to control the robot
